OL,6,FMairi MacRae, Shelter's director of
OL,7,Fcampaigns, policy and communications,
OL,8,Ftold ITV News that households being
OL,9,Fmoved between temporary accommodation
OL,10,Fcan affect a child's education.
OL,12,FShe said some children have had to
OL,13,Fmiss school because of it.
OL,15,F'Every possible way you can imagine,
OL,16,Fit's impacting children,' says
OL,17,FShelter's Mairi MacRae
OL,19,F"No child should face the trauma of
OL,20,Fgrowing up homeless," she said.
