OL,6,F"With skyrocketing rents, and with a
OL,7,Flack of truly affordable social homes,
OL,8,Fwe see more and more families being
OL,9,Fforced into insecure and temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,F"What that looks like is often one-
OL,13,Fbedroom B&Bs, grotty hostels, people
OL,14,Fsharing beds, no kitchen, sharing
OL,15,Fbathrooms with strangers, living out
OL,16,Fof a suitcase, and feeling very
OL,17,Fanxious about being moved away at
OL,18,Fshort notice."
