OL,6,FA total of 90 households with children
OL,7,Fhad been in bed and breakfast
OL,8,Faccommodation for at least five years,
OL,9,Fthe latest figures showed, up from 60
OL,10,Fthe previous year.
OL,12,FPolly Neate, chief executive of
OL,13,Fhomelessness charity Shelter, has
OL,14,Fcalled on the government to offer more
OL,15,Fsupport.
OL,17,FShe said: "No child should have to
OL,18,Fface the trauma of growing up
OL,19,Fhomeless. The housing emergency has
OL,20,Ftrapped many families in temporary
OL,21,Faccommodation for over five years."
