OL,6,FThe number of households with children
OL,7,Fthat were either at risk of
OL,8,Fhomelessness or already homeless rose
OL,9,Fby 3.9%.
OL,11,FThe number of single households
OL,12,Fassessed as rough sleeping has
OL,13,Fincreased by 14.2%.
