OL,4,Cthan 12% in past year
OL,6,FIt is calling on the government to end
OL,7,Fthe 'Care Cliff' - which leaves many
OL,8,Fyoung people homeless on the night of
OL,9,Ftheir 18th birthday.
OL,11,FThe number of young care leavers aged
OL,12,F18-20 who are homeless has increased
OL,13,Fby 54% over the last five years,
OL,14,Faccording to analysis by Become.
OL,16,FAmy Charles says she had an "unstable"
OL,17,Fupbringing and moved between homes.
