OL,6,F"Young people leaving care are quite
OL,7,Fvulnerable, they don't have the family
OL,8,Fsupport that other young people have
OL,9,Faround them," she told ITV News.
OL,11,F"There are housing pressures, cost of
OL,12,Fliving pressures and we are seeing
OL,13,Fhuge pressure on local authority
OL,14,Fbudgets, meaning there is less support
OL,15,Foften for young people leaving care."
OL,17,FSome young people can stay with their
OL,18,Ffoster family for a little bit longer
OL,19,Fafter they turn 18, but for too many
OL,20,Fpeople that is not an option.
