OL,6,F'This is a national scandal,' says
OL,7,FBecome CEO Katharine Sacks-Jones
OL,9,F"These are young people who have been
OL,10,Fthrough a huge amount of trauma," she
OL,11,Fexplained.
OL,13,F"Far far too many of them are starting
OL,14,Ftheir adult life becoming homeless."
